{"tid":675293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[手作JJ ] 做金工不停揼手指","createTime":"2018-05-23T11:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T13:21:20.000Z","uid":150698,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"932c3909097bd2f891b86bf3cf4642f8ed9bcc5a","tid":675293,"uid":150698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近排失戀又厭食<br />\n<br />\n迷上左做金工<br />\n一上手就揼揼揼 <br />\n身邊啲人俾我嚇親<br />\n<br />\n幻想下有條友六個鐘不停打塊鐵<br />\n有時候仲一度揼一度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到依加都未送上青山 我都算好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日又不停揼中手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比例又揼唔好<br />\n力度唔平均<br />\n俾人話我有雜念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n失戀真係累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 冇乜食嘢都可以打咁耐 下下出盡力<br />\n可見人係究極狀態可以有幾咁大嘅潛能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/194103_3c80116d4290d896ffbc83d613a8583b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F194103_3c80116d4290d896ffbc83d613a8583b.png&h=85cc23d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頂你個肺 連條邊都打得柒過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d9f33a9cbe35c14376efe46b6ed4fe9d199d14","tid":675293,"uid":150400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c96d62d0d299d5de06ecfa92c7c5ad